   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-accepting-acceptted" mid="53" select_type="3" />
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>So you sent me to Kahlua on purpose when you already knew about the codes?!!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-a" mid="55" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>As I've said before, jewel hunt is not forbidden by law in Merca. All I have to say is that the Anti-Goddess lady was unlucky to be involved in this. Unfortunately, I'm sure even the Anti-Goddess Faction would not want to make Tryan an overt enemy at times like this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-b" mid="56" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>…After Rubinart and Geraint disappeared… I thought you're the only one I could trust...</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-c" mid="57" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="8"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Aww, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.<BR>I am NOT you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-1-d" mid="58" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9712_qu_01.ogg}<BR>Have I ever promised you a bright future? Did I give you trust and ask you to follow me without any worries? It's rather selfish of you to view this as a betrayal when you're seeing everything in your own perspective. You don't think about how this is going to put me in a difficult situation which may possibly ruin my relationship with Tryan.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2" mid="59" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="10"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(It looks like I can't ask for help from him. I should go to </FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Hiver's house</FONT><FONT color=#662500> myself!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1826_Kahlua-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Scholar_Baily.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1826_Kahlua-1-" mid="60" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>I have nothing… So I have no fears… And nothing to leave behind when I die… Ah… No… It's not that there wasn't anything to lose… Ah...<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Hiver sobs as she sings an awful song.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-2-" mid="61" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>I hope you don't do anything foolish. If you meet one of Tryan's men who remembers your face, everything can go wrong!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-a" mid="63" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>Everything is over….<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Hiver looks dumbfounded.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-b" mid="64" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#2b2723>${user_nick}$<BR></FONT><FONT color=#662500>What…?! What happened, Hiver?! What just happened here?!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-c" mid="65" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>I heard from my youngest sister that strange men started appearing near our house. I thought it was because of me… I thought they found out that I was in the <FONT color=#a82424>Anti-Goddess Faction</FONT>… So I thought I should stay away from my house as much as I could...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-d" mid="66" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>But that was not the case… The man I let into my barn out of foolish sympathy… no, it was because I lost my sense of judgement seeing how much he looked like Guy… I shouldn't have let him into our barn... He was a <FONT color=#a82424>Child</FONT> that occurred not long ago…</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-e" mid="67" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>(I knew it! Vernicka knew everything and wanted to send me somewhere else to prevent trouble!)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-e" image="QW_Tryan.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-f" mid="69" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver${sound:npc_Hiver_9712_qu_01.ogg}<BR>While I was away, <FONT color=#a82424>Tryan</FONT> and his soldiers barged in, and the battle between the Childs devastated the whole area...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-f" image="QN_Grele.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-g" mid="70" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="19"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Where's Grele? How about your parents? Are your other siblings okay?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-h" mid="71" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>My parents and siblings were already dead when I got here… It seemed almost like they were asleep… Maybe that really is the case… They are comfortably in their eternal sleep now that their pain is over… The funny thing is that Grele was working in the carpet factory and that saved his life... Does it even make sense? He sacrificed himself to earn money and that saved his life... You just die when you don't work hard in this world... Hahaha...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-i" mid="72" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Hiver…!</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-j" mid="73" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver${sound:npc_Hiver_9712_qu_02.ogg}<BR>……I shouldn't have trusted anyone….<BR>They are not me… This world is not Lagendia. It's Mistland, a land of nightmares……….!!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-k" mid="74" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>I can't even complain about it anywhere! <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>, you must have realised it by now that this world is ruled by the Childs. Even though Merca calls itself a free neutral city, it has no choice but to keep its mouth shut in a conflict between Childs and commoners. What on earth are those Childs?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-l" mid="75" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>No one knows how they are formed. We just know that they suddenly appear like a disaster and the Childs call that an Awakening. Since they are an evolved form of the Beyond Dragon, maybe they awaken from the dragon. Whatever it is, maybe it would have been better if I was born a Child too. Then... Then...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-l" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-m" mid="76" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Hiver stares blankly at the sky like she has no more strength.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-m" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-n" mid="77" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver${sound:npc_Hiver_9712_qu_03.ogg}<BR>……But isn't it funny…? I still want to save this world… I want to save the people suffering in pain...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-n" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-o" mid="78" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>According to a story told in the Anti-Goddess Faction, the people in the original world created by Goddess <FONT color=#a82424>Vestinel</FONT> had no feelings. They lived their lives like puppets and didn't feel any pain either. What the <FONT color=#a82424>Great God Desmodeus</FONT> felt most appalled by Vestinel's world was the unnatural way its constituents behaved more than how perverse the whole world was.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-o" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-p" mid="79" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>……Why didn't she just leave us as puppets without feelings…? Why did she have to copy Lagendia…? Was she so jealous about Lagendia which was filled with laughter and joy...?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-p" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-q" mid="80" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver${sound:npc_Hiver_9712_qu_04.ogg}<BR>They get hurt… betrayed… lose someone… and despair… but then again, they dream of happiness again...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-q" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-r" mid="81" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>It must sound strange but I don't think <FONT color=#a82424>Goddess Altea</FONT> is a beautiful and harmonious goddess… Maybe she was just lonely… Too lonely that she needed a world that she could love and be loved by… That's what's been in my mind...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-r" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-s" mid="82" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Hiver……….</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-s" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-t" mid="83" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>……I should come back to my senses. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Hiver pulls herself together.)</FONT><BR>Tryan and his men must still be keeping an eye on this area. I heard the Child who was hiding in my barn was not caught.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-t" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-u" mid="84" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>Did you do anything that might reveal your identity to Tryan while helping President Vernicka?<BR>If so, you should leave this place quickly, <FONT color=#387206>{user_nick}</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-2-u" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-3" mid="85" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>Oh don't look at me like that. I still have <FONT color=#a82424>Guy and Grele</FONT>.<BR>I need to retrieve my parents' and my siblings' bodies too… They can finally rest together beside my other siblings who starved to death when they were young...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1815_cradle_hiver-3" image="QN_Vernicka.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Right_hiver.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1815_cradle_hiver-3-" mid="87" select_type="5" />
      <talk_question mid="35"><![CDATA[<html>$Hiver$<BR>Now, please. Go back to <FONT color=#a82424>President Vernicka</FONT>. When I'm done here, I'll go to <FONT color=#a82424>Merca's Heart</FONT> so please meet me there.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" mid="89" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka$<BR>Welcome back. I heard <FONT color=#a82424>Tryan</FONT> already made his trip there. I hope you didn't create any trouble...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" mid="90" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>…I…I just don't understand.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n1816_vernicka-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="Npc_Left_vernicka.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n1816_vernicka-3-c" mid="91" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$President Vernicka${sound:npc_Vernicka_9712_qu_02.ogg}<BR>This world is full of things you can't understand.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
